description: Erection of buildings ranging in height from three-storeys to five-storeys for a residential development comprising of 30 affordable units (to include 7 x 4-bedroom house, 6 x 3-bedroom flats, 13 x 2-bedroom flats and 4 x 1-bedroom flats), with new vehicular accesses and, associated ball court, landscaping and playspace, car parking, bicycle stores and bin stores
